Welcome to The Tyler, East Haven's Newest Apartment Community for Adults 55+
Nestled in a residential neighborhood, The Tyler is East Haven’s newest apartment community for adults age 55+.  A handsome landmark that once served as the East Haven High School and is now listed on the National Register of Historic Places, has been reintroduced as modern apartment living available now!  Learn more about our innovative community here.Read More  Nestled in a residential neighborhood, The Tyler is East Haven’s newest apartment community for adults age 55+.  A handsome landmark that once served as the East Haven High School and is now listed on the National Register of Historic Places, has been reintroduced as modern apartment living available now!  Learn more about our innovative community here.Come experience the new stylish and sophisticated look of the historic former East Haven High School. Choose from beautifully planned one and two bedroom apartment homes featuring tall ceilings, over-sized windows, fully appointed kitchens with rich walnut wood cabinets and slate-look flooring.  Residents of The Tyler will enjoy the convenience of an on site laundry care center plus an impressive amenity package including fitness center, lounge with hosted social activities, a crafting room, indoor and outdoor gathering areas, dedicated on-site parking and on-site management. We look forward to making The Tyler your new home! Read Less 

Contact us to learn more!
